Sentencas: An issue associated with chromia-scale formation on ferritic stainless steels is an associated increase in electrical resistance over time, due to the oxide growth.
Titulo: Oxidation and Electrical Behavior of Mn-Co-Coated Crofer 22 APU Steel Produced by a Pack Cementation Method for SOFC Interconnect Applications

Sentencas: Further, the migration of chromium via chromia-scale evaporation into solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) cathodes can result in degradation in cell electrochemical performance.
Titulo: Oxidation and Electrical Behavior of Mn-Co-Coated Crofer 22 APU Steel Produced by a Pack Cementation Method for SOFC Interconnect Applications

Sentencas: In this research, manganese and cobalt were deposited by the pack cementation method onto Crofer 22 APU ferritic stainless steel.
Titulo: Oxidation and Electrical Behavior of Mn-Co-Coated Crofer 22 APU Steel Produced by a Pack Cementation Method for SOFC Interconnect Applications

Sentencas: Isothermal and cyclic oxidation was carried out to evaluate the role of coating materials during oxidation.
Titulo: Oxidation and Electrical Behavior of Mn-Co-Coated Crofer 22 APU Steel Produced by a Pack Cementation Method for SOFC Interconnect Applications

Sentencas: Area-specific resistance (ASR) of the Mn-Co-coated substrates was also tested at 800 A degrees C.
Titulo: Oxidation and Electrical Behavior of Mn-Co-Coated Crofer 22 APU Steel Produced by a Pack Cementation Method for SOFC Interconnect Applications

Sentencas: The results demonstrate that the coating layer transforms to MnCo2O4, CoFe2O4, CoCr2O4, and Co3O4 spinels during oxidation.
Titulo: Oxidation and Electrical Behavior of Mn-Co-Coated Crofer 22 APU Steel Produced by a Pack Cementation Method for SOFC Interconnect Applications

Sentencas: This scale is protective, and acts as an effective barrier against chromium migration into the outer oxide.
Titulo: Oxidation and Electrical Behavior of Mn-Co-Coated Crofer 22 APU Steel Produced by a Pack Cementation Method for SOFC Interconnect Applications

Sentencas: Mn-Co oxide and cobalt oxides also cause a reduction in ASR, in comparison to that of bare steel.
